TROST, Respondent, v. HINMAN, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 15, 1893.) Action by Evelyn M. Trost against Charles J. Hinman.

Argued before VAN BRUNT, P. J., and O’BRIEN and PARKER, JJ.

Horace Graves, for appellant. S. A. & D. J. Noyes, (Alex. Thain, of counsel,) for respondent.

(No opinion. Judgment affirmed. See 22 N. Y. Supp. 612.
